        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 22–29. Potamonautes obesus (A. Milne­Edwards, 1868), adult male, form II (cw 49.1 mm, NMU TRW 1968.06) from Mlali, near Morogoro, Uluguru Mountains, Tanzania. 22, left gonopod 1, dorsal aspect; 23, left gonopod 1, terminal article, superior aspect; 24, left gonopod 1, ventral aspect. Potamonautes calcaratus (Gordon, 1929), lectotype, adult male, form I (cw 35.8 mm, NHML 1929.3.5.9–13). 25, left gonopod 1, dorsal aspect; 26, left gonopod 1, terminal article, superior aspect; 27, left gonopod 1, ventral aspect." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/5027908/files/figure.png" .

